Model-View-Controller for bank complaint system

In a bank complaint system, a customer can input a complaint, where the support person is able to resolve their issue.

Considered Options
Model-View-Controller 
Service oriented architecture
Three tier architecture
…
Decision Outcome
Chosen option: "Model-View-Controller", because model handles data and business logic, the view manages presentation which is important for how the interface is presented to the users, the controller handles user input and connects the model and view.

Consequences
Good, because each part of the application will have its own job, which is useful as it reduces redundancy and ensures all basis are covered.
Bad, because can slow down development as theres more to set up which is time consuming.
…
